headline.print_headline: Langdon Wins NHRA Thunder Valley Nationals
headline.main: Langdon Wins NHRA Thunder Valley Nationals

lead_paragraph: Defending Top Fuel champion Shawn Langdon raced to his first victory of the season Sunday, beating points leader Doug Kalitta in the NHRA Thunder Valley Nationals.
